* '''Komainu''' (Tangible Cultural Property, Sculpture)

== Subsidiary Shrines ==
The shrine grounds also host three subsidiary shrines:
* '''Suwa Shrine''' - Deities: {{ill|Takeminakata|ja|建御名方神|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeminakata|qq=}}, {{ill|Ōkuninushi|ja|大国主神|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōkuninushi|qq=}}
* '''Tenjin Shrine''' - deity: {{ill|Tenjin (kami)|ja|天満天神|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenjin (kami)|qq=}}
* '''Okuno Shrine''' - deity: Okuno Saemon Koreyoshi Kyo

