* '''Tenjin Shrine''' - deity: {{ill|Tenjin (kami)|ja|天満天神|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenjin (kami)|qq=}}
* '''Okuno Shrine''' - deity: Okuno Saemon Koreyoshi Kyo

